+### Full Reporting Spec
+
+# Session Report Schema
+
+## Location
+
+`.bot/{branchName}/report.json` â€” one per branch, all bots append.
+
+## JSON Structure
+
+```json
+{
+  "branch": "branch-name",
+  "sessions": [
+    {
+      "id": "UUID",
+      "bot": "coder|architect|web|marketing",
+      "timestamp_start": "ISO 8601",
